* Richard Garner and Steve Lack, [https://arxiv.org/abs/1108.2934 "On the axioms for adhesive and quasiadhesive categories"], ''Theory and Applications of Categories'', Vol. 27, 2012, No. 3, pp 27–46.
* Steve Lack and Pawel Sobocinski, [http://users.ecs.soton.ac.uk/ps/papers/toposesAdhesive.pdf "Toposes are adhesive"].
* Steve Lack, [http://www.tac.mta.ca/tac/volumes/25/7/25-07abs.html "An embedding theorem for adhesive categories"], ''Theory and Applications of Categories'', Vol. 25, 2011, No. 7, pp 180–188.

